des: "Frozen daiquiris are a great way to cool off on a hot summer day. Blend rum, sugar, triple sec, and lime juice together with ice for a frosty cocktail treat."
ins:
Combine light rum, triple sec, lime juice, and ice in blender with 1 cup crushed ice; blend until smooth. Pour into  a Champagne flute.
Garnish with maraschino cherry.
